App.xaml
App.xaml.cs
*.sln
*.csproj

# Claude Code / agent config (local-only project memory + rules)
.claude/
.github/copilot-instructions.md

# Build outputs
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

