.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

# Test results
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*

